title: Ticket Presale For WWE Saturday Night’s Main Event, Punk vs. McIntyre, Cody vs. Roman, More
text: The ticket presale for the upcoming return of WWE Saturday Night’s Main Event is underway. The presale code for the show is SATURDAY. On Saturday, December 4, WWE Saturday Night’s Main Event will be back at the Nassau Coliseum in Uniondale, New York. It will be broadcast live on NBC. Tickets can be purchased now at [Ticketmaster](https://www.ticketmaster.com/wwe-saturday-nights-main-event-uniondale-new-york-12-14-2024/event/0000611EC5B88E7E?lid=8psm0vo7rorq). WWE CCO Paul “Triple H” Levesque also announced another presale code WWE2024 on social media. He tweeted, “This is going to be special. Use presale code WWE2024 to make sure you’re there LIVE for the return of Saturday Night’s Main Event on Dec. 14 at @NassauColiseum.” This is going to be special. Use presale code WWE2024 to make sure you’re there LIVE for the return of Saturday Night’s Main Event on Dec. 14 at [@NassauColiseum].
